Subject: Re: [T2] Switching from 4speed to Auto - what parts needed ?

On Tue, 22 Jan 2002 Oldschoolvw(-at-)aol.com wrote:

check the archives this has been gone over with several times.
. frames are slightly different
. different accel linkages
. different mounts (tranny front)
. floor at shifter different
. different shift linkage mounts
. accelerator is on different side of engine. (sort of)

also the 73 auto tranny is a vacuum shift and needs lines to manifold, try
to get late model tranny (75-79) it has a vacuum shift and parts are still
mostly avaliable.

Bob


